    "Ms are trained to produce molecular strings element-by-element and have fast generation capabilities.",
    "However, the iterative structure forces those models to compress the sequence into an information bottleneck and challenges the learning of global sequence properties [23] [24] [25].",
    "Transformers 26, a more recent architecture, overcome this bottleneck by processing the entire input molecular string at once 27, 28.",
